\id 1TI - Uare
\h 1Timoteo
\toc3 1Tim
\toc2 1Timoteo
\toc1 Timoteo veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Ibiꞌa
\mt1 1Timoteo
\mt2 Timoteo veize Pauloꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Ibiꞌa
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa
\ip Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe Pauloꞌa Timoteo veize mirihiro. Timoteo mogaꞌe Giriki vazeḡa zu viꞌaꞌe Iuda roḡaeḡa. Timoteoꞌe Paulo teite harame ragaveꞌenaꞌa, ani dananiro. Pauloꞌa ibite Timoteo teite Efeso ekalesia veize gauiro ebu Timoteoꞌa ze ibitozoga veize ani eꞌea modiro. Timoteoꞌe Efeso ekalesia veize gaueꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano Pauloꞌa soꞌa ꞌahi mirihiro. Eꞌe madaḡano ḡuriro ihore azaḡaniꞌa ekalesia tutuze veꞌorinu ꞌahine, Pauloꞌa zeḡe ihoreꞌe veꞌoḡa rae fureniro, zu ekalesia azaḡaꞌe zeḡe ḡoere ago hegotoꞌi rae ihoziro. Ebu ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe nougenouge raditeꞌe zu nougenouge gauiteꞌe moneo ḡoeriro. Ebu Iesu Keriso tuḡure vazeḡa manoḡa rouga veize zu ekalesia azaḡa nunu veize nougenouge gauiteꞌe moneo Timoteo iraduguniro.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Eḡe, Pauloꞌa soꞌa ꞌadi miriheꞌohe. Badiꞌaꞌe emeḡe ḡabofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, zu Keriso Iesuꞌe emeꞌa fieꞌenaꞌa guhine radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Badiꞌa zu Iesuꞌa eḡe ohotadu eꞌe Keriso Iesu apostolo vazeḡano reiro.
\p 
\v 2 Soꞌa ꞌadiꞌe Timoteo, ḡae mazao miriheꞌohe. Ḡaꞌe hube hune eḡe ubude, mazaḡa eꞌa ḡae mazao haramadu ḡae zuni Iesu mazao firo.
\p Badiꞌa emeḡe Mama zu emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Keriso Iesuꞌa ḡae mazao manoḡa zu vetuḡa ebu zama roḡeḡa ḡaneꞌenoꞌi.
\s1 Ḡuriro Ihore Azaḡa mazao Riḡa Iraduguziro
\p 
\v 3 E Makedonia habaꞌa uꞌa iḡunirotene inare ḡeiroteꞌe teige, ḡa Efeso zamaḡano radoꞌi. Eꞌea radiuꞌenaꞌa, vaze nuꞌa ḡurire ihoreḡa ihozeꞌeteꞌe gararoꞌi.
\v 4 Ebu ze amahi irihineḡa zu vouḡaze ni moneo mene ufeta zamare gauifine riḡa ḡorezoꞌi. ꞌUguḡaniꞌa taꞌiro fureneꞌohe, ebu Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ḡabozoga veize Badiꞌaꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe gauḡa moneo mene hune ihozeꞌohe.
\v 5 Eḡeꞌa ꞌahige riḡa ihoꞌeꞌetaꞌaꞌe vazeꞌa zamarotitoga veize raꞌohe. Vaze zamarotitogaꞌe zama deheḡanonoꞌo zu duduḡa rae zamareꞌeteꞌe haḡaeꞌeteꞌeanoꞌo zu ihore huga hube hune mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌeanoꞌo fureruꞌohe.
\v 6 Rehano vaze nu'e ihore huga ꞌadi modadu huga o'oꞌano taꞌirotiteꞌeteꞌe hegoteꞌohe.
\v 7 Ze'e Mose goro ḡoe'a ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa reihi raꞌohe. Rehano ze zeḡeꞌa bare nagini raꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa, ebu zeꞌa hube hune rae raꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa moneo zuni aḡuꞌa.
\p 
\v 8 Eme edeḡa, vaze'a ibi duduḡano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa hegotine, Mose goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe manoḡa.
\v 9 Rehano eme edeḡa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe duduḡa azaḡa veize mene haḡairo. Aꞌe goro ḡoeꞌa varadeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, Badiꞌa mene hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, Badiꞌa mene gubaneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, sauꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, Badiꞌa ḡoereo mene zaḡozaḡeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, Badiꞌa mazao mene kurauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, viꞌa moga ga vaze goruzeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa,
\v 10 ubuma ḡezo azaḡa, ohozeꞌa ohoze teite zu roḡaeꞌa roḡae teite daroeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, vaze oboze teadu serozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, ḡurireꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, kotao ḡurireꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, ebu ihore duduḡa hezahohauꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa nunu hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa veize haḡairo.
\v 11 Ihore hugaꞌe Iesu hari manoḡanonoꞌo ariro. Hari manoḡa aꞌe emeꞌa niguneꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa rae furenadu eḡeꞌa vaze ihozifine iniro.
\s1 Badiꞌaꞌa Paulo Vetuḡaniro.
\p 
\v 12 Keriso Iesu emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa inarahiroteꞌe moneo eḡeꞌa ani mazao manoḡa tauḡi raꞌohe, mazaḡa aniꞌa e hube hune ani mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rae zamaradu ane gau haḡaifine ohohiro.
\v 13 E ibite Iesu rae sausauniro, zu ani hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa aduga ziniro, zu utiutiḡa reiro. Rehano e ani mazao mene firoteꞌe madaḡano ani aḡuꞌa radu ꞌouge haḡairoteꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌaꞌa eḡe vetuḡahiro.
\v 14 Emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌaꞌa manoḡa borofe iniro ꞌahine, e Keriso Iesu teite tiburanadu ani mazao fie gigaruꞌohe, ebu ani zu vaze zamare borofeꞌohe.
\p 
\v 15 “Keriso Iesuꞌa sauꞌa azaḡa ḡabozoga veize raha ꞌadi ariro,” rae raꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe huga, zu vaze niduꞌa mae ḡihiniteꞌe ḡoeꞌa. Ebu eꞌe sauꞌa azaḡa boꞌaḡano ufeta sauꞌa hune vazeḡa.
\v 16 Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa vetuḡahiro. Aꞌe, ufeta sauꞌa hune vazeḡa, eḡe veize Keriso Iesuꞌa mada faḡa zamaḡa obone tirotaꞌaꞌe vaze niduꞌa ihozifine, ebu zeḡe zuni ane mazao fiadu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidifine raꞌohe.
\v 17 Radiu tuḡutuḡu Kiniḡa, mene rudatiteꞌe zu mene horoneꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa tibuhuga gubanihi ebu niḡa mae ḡihinihi, onamo tuḡutuḡu! Amen.
\s1 Pauloꞌa Timoteo Inaraniro
\p 
\v 18 Timoteo, eḡe ubude, ibite vazeꞌa ḡae moneo Badiꞌa ḡoere rae fureniroteꞌe idunaḡano, eḡeꞌa ḡoere ꞌahi ihoꞌeꞌohe. Ḡa zeꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌenaꞌa, Keriso hari manoḡa veize faine utitoꞌi.
\v 19 Ihore huga mae ḡihinoꞌi, zu naginiꞌe duduḡa ga veꞌoḡa rae faine zamaradu duduḡa daꞌo haḡaoꞌi. Vaze nuꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare zamaroneze duduḡa hezahoharo zu ḡasiꞌa fahau zubureꞌeteꞌe teige, zeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌeꞌa dauḡiro.
\v 20 Zeḡe boꞌaḡano Himenaio zu Alesanaꞌe eḡeꞌa Satani ꞌevoreo riꞌiziro. Ze aduga hidadu Badiꞌa mene bare rae sausaunoga veize eḡeꞌa ihozihi reiro.
\c 2
\s1 Nougenouge Kurauꞌeteꞌe moneo Ihoniro
\p 
\v 1 Eꞌanoꞌo e ibite geno ḡoere ꞌahi inare ḡaꞌohe. Vaze niduꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa Badiꞌa mazao umidoꞌi, zu zeḡe veize kuranoꞌi, zu vaze ꞌahogaꞌahoga veize kuranoꞌi, ebu zeḡe niduꞌa veize Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi roꞌi.
\v 2 Nize boro azaḡa niduꞌa ebu kini veize kuranoꞌi. ꞌOugine, eme Badiꞌa hube hune gubaneꞌenaꞌa zu zaḡozaḡe haḡaeꞌenaꞌa, zama roḡeḡa huneo sifu radiꞌuma.
\v 3 ꞌOuge kurauꞌetaꞌaꞌe manoḡa, zu emeḡe ḡabofeꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa matuꞌohauꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa.
\v 4 Badiꞌaꞌe vaze niduꞌa ḡabone hidoga zu zeꞌe ihore huga ederadu mae ḡihinoga urateꞌohe.
\v 5 Badiꞌaꞌe tibuhuga, ebu Badiꞌa zu vaze boꞌaḡano nema vazeḡa zuni tibuhuga. Aniꞌe vaze, Keriso Iesu.
\v 6 Aniꞌa vaze niduꞌa haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo bohaze buzoga veize ane bare dibuꞌiro. Ebu ani Badiꞌaꞌa ohoniroteꞌe madaḡano ꞌouge haḡadu Badiꞌaꞌa vaze ḡaboziteꞌe rae fureniro.
\v 7 Hari manoḡa eꞌe rae furenifine, Badiꞌaꞌa eꞌe haramo vazeḡano zu apostolo vazeḡano ohohiro. Ebu Iuda mene azaḡa mazao hari manoḡa huga ihozadu ze Iesu mazao fioga veize, e zeḡe ihore vazeḡano ohohiro. E huga ḡoereꞌohe zu mene ḡurireꞌohe.
\p 
\v 8 E ohozeohozeꞌa haba niduꞌa zamaḡano Badiꞌa mazao kuranoga urateꞌohe. Ebu ze mene maḡuneꞌenaꞌa, mene roteteꞌenaꞌa, zu zaḡozaḡe radiuꞌenaꞌa, ꞌevoreze mae ḡihinadu kuranoga e urateꞌohe.
\v 9 Ebu roḡaeroḡae zuni dabua idaidaḡa faine vidanoga, iguze mene nunufe siꞌoga, ebu hadi naeḡa boro zu naeḡa boro dabuaḡa mene vidanoga urateꞌohe.
\v 10 U ze haḡai manoḡa haḡadu ze zeḡeꞌa bare Badiꞌa gubaneꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡa rae furenoga urateꞌohe.
\v 11 Roḡaeꞌe ihore azaḡa ꞌuꞌuḡano ḡoereze niduꞌa egohanadu sifu edeḡa meꞌuma.
\v 12 E roḡaeꞌa ohoze ihozoga zu ibitozoga mene idaḡa raꞌohe. Ze sifu radiꞌuma.
\v 13 Mazaḡa Adamuꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ibite haḡairo ebu hena Eva haḡairo.
\v 14 Sataniꞌa Adamu mene soꞌoniro, rehano Eva soꞌonadu aniꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡairo.
\v 15 Rehano roḡaeꞌa iḡaiḡa Iesu mazao fieꞌenaꞌa, vaze zamare borofine ebu zaḡozaḡeꞌenaꞌa faine radiune, zeꞌa ene fureneꞌeteꞌeanoꞌo\f + \fr 2:15 \fqa zeꞌa ene furenadu taufeꞌeteꞌeanoꞌo \f* Badiꞌaꞌa ḡaboziꞌuma.
\c 3
\s1 Ekalesia Ibitoziꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa Haḡai
\p 
\v 1 Ḡoere ꞌahiꞌe huga: Iniu ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa reihi rae raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe gau manoḡa tauḡi haḡaihi reꞌuma.
\v 2 Eꞌanoꞌo ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe vazeꞌa veꞌoḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa mene haḡaiꞌuma, inuga tiba daꞌo meꞌuma, faine zamareꞌenaꞌa gauiꞌuma, aneꞌa bare haḡai sauꞌa hezahohaꞌuma, aniꞌe vazeꞌa gubaniꞌuma, iꞌudo azaḡa mae zouzadu ḡubuziꞌuma, zu vaze faine ihozogaꞌe idaḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa reꞌuma.
\v 3 Aniꞌe vu sauꞌa mene ufeta gagiꞌuma zu mene utiutiḡa reꞌuma, rehano roḡeru haḡaiꞌuma, mene rotetiꞌuma, zu hadi ubumaḡa mene reꞌuma.
\v 4 Aniꞌa ane neo tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa faine ibitoziꞌuma zu ubugaubuganiꞌa hube hune ani gubaneꞌenaꞌa ani ḡoere egohafine ihoziꞌuma.
\v 5 Iniu ane neo tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mene faine ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe nougenouge ekalesia ibitoziꞌuma?
\v 6 Ekalesia izigaꞌe ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa iḡurio mene ohoniꞌuma. Aniꞌe iḡuri eꞌe meine, aneꞌa bare niḡa mae itadu Badiꞌaꞌa Diabolo kotaniroteꞌe teige, ani zuni kotaniꞌuma gaogi.
\v 7 Ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mene ekalesia azaḡaniꞌa zuni gubaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa reꞌuma. ꞌOugine, zeꞌa ani mene rae sausauniꞌuma zu Diabolo ꞌahirio ani mene ꞌahiriniꞌuma.
\s1 Diakono Azaḡa Haḡai
\p 
\v 8 Diakono azaḡa zuni ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teige vazeꞌa gubazeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa reꞌuma, ḡoere huga daꞌo reꞌuma, vu sauꞌa mene ufeta gagiꞌuma, zu hadi ubumaḡa mene reꞌuma.
\v 9 Ze zama deheḡa hina duduḡa daꞌo zamareꞌenaꞌa, Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌuꞌuru teadu rae fureniroteꞌe ihoreḡa huga ꞌaune mae ḡihiniꞌuma.
\v 10 Vaze ꞌizema ohozogano ze faine udahiꞌuma ebu zeḡe mazao veꞌoḡa oꞌoꞌa reine, diakono iḡurio ohoziꞌuma.
\v 11 Diakono azaḡa teige, inudeze zuni vazeꞌa gubazeꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡa reꞌuma, vaze mene rae sausauziꞌuma, faine zamareꞌenaꞌa gauiꞌuma, zu gau niduꞌaꞌe zamaze niduꞌa hina haḡaiꞌuma.
\v 12 Diakono azaḡa zuni inuga tiba daꞌo meꞌuma, ebu ane ubugaubuga zu ane neo tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa faine ibitoziꞌuma.
\v 13 Diakono gauḡa faine haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe vazeꞌa nize mae ḡihiniꞌuma, ebu ze zeḡeꞌa Keriso Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe moneo ufeta borofe rae fureniꞌuma. \fig Ne tiba azaḡaniꞌa kurauꞌohe|src="AP-08-06.TIF" size="col" ref="3:1-12"\fig*
\s1 Badiꞌaꞌa Ihore Huga rae Fureniro
\p 
\v 14 E ḡarihe amihi rehano, izidi ḡae mazao ḡoeꞌa ꞌahi miriheꞌohe,
\v 15 mazaḡa e mene ḡarihe amine, vazeꞌa Badiꞌa mone nego nabudi boꞌaḡano nougenouge haḡae raditeꞌe moneo ḡa ihoꞌifine raꞌohe. Badiꞌa mone nego nabudiꞌe ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa mazao fieꞌeteꞌe ekalesiaḡa. Ebu ne ogoruꞌetene raha huꞌi sebanadu gado ohoneꞌeteꞌe teige, zeꞌe ḡoere huga rana edau gigaruꞌohe.
\v 16 Zuhiꞌa Boro mazao kurauꞌenaꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe ḡaboneḡa moneo Badiꞌaꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune. Vaze niduꞌa ḡoere aꞌe huga raꞌohe:
\q1 Aniꞌe vazeo fureraro,
\q2 Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa aniꞌe duduḡa rae fureniro,
\q1 aniꞌe tuḡure vigaviganiꞌa horoniro,
\q2 vazeꞌa ani moneo habaꞌahabaꞌano haramiro,
\q1 raha azaḡaniꞌa ani mazao firo,
\q2 ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ani adure ḡoha mae itadu eꞌea aniꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune rae reiro.
\c 4
\s1 Ḡuriro Ihoreḡa Azaḡa
\p 
\v 1 Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ꞌahige deheru raꞌohe. Vesu vaze nuꞌa ihore huga mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe modadu soꞌosoꞌo viga zu vine sauꞌa ihoreḡa hegotiꞌuma.
\v 2 Ihore ꞌuguḡaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa ḡuriro ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo areꞌohe. Ze aḡuꞌa, zeḡe zamaroneꞌe auri gigiꞌaḡa hina hufiroteꞌe teige rudanadu zeḡe ihoreꞌe veꞌoḡa.
\v 3 Ze vaze mazao, “Ago hahuroꞌi,” ebu “Ogomu nuꞌe ago anoꞌi,” rae raꞌohe. Rehano ogomu ꞌuguḡaꞌe Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe zu ihore huga edereꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi radu anoga veize Badiꞌaꞌa haḡadu rifiro.
\v 4 Mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa haḡairoteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe manoḡa. Eme ani mazao manoḡa tauḡi radu eꞌe aune, ḡauni ꞌahoga mene hezahohaꞌuma.
\v 5 Mazaḡa Badiꞌa ḡoere ebu emeꞌa ogomu veize manoḡa tauḡi rae kurauꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, ogomu nidu'aꞌe zaḡoḡa.
\s1 Iesu Keriso veize Gaueꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa Manoḡa
\p 
\v 6 Ḡa eḡe ḡoere ꞌadi nego nabudi faine ihozoꞌi. ꞌOugine, ḡaꞌa mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa huga zu hegoteꞌeteꞌe ihoreḡa huga hina ufeta ḡuhuradu Keriso Iesu veize gaueꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa manoḡa reꞌuma.
\v 7 Badiꞌa rae sausauneꞌeteꞌe ḡuriro hariḡa zu vouḡaze irihine hezahohanoꞌi. Rehano Badiꞌa gubaneꞌenaꞌa radoga veize ḡa ḡae bare taufoꞌi.
\v 8 Ahiri faine taufine, manoḡa nu meꞌuma. Rehano Badiꞌa gubaneꞌenaꞌa radiune, ḡau niduꞌa ibiḡano manoḡa hidiꞌuma. Manoḡa aꞌe izidi madaḡano zu zama moneo Badiꞌaꞌa rifiꞌuma rae ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡaboneḡa.
\v 9 Ḡoere aꞌe huga, zu vaze niduꞌa mae ḡihiniteꞌe ḡoeꞌa.
\v 10 Eme Badiꞌaꞌa ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡaboneḡa hidifine, ḡihau gaue inareꞌohe, mazaḡa emeꞌe ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡaniꞌa eꞌe rifiꞌuma rae mae ḡihineꞌohe. Aniꞌe vaze niduꞌa ḡabozeꞌeteꞌe zu ani mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ufeta hune ḡabozeꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa.
\p 
\v 11 Za ihore ꞌadi riḡa zoꞌi ebu ihozoꞌi.
\v 12 Ḡaꞌe tahiꞌa iziga radu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ḡa ovoe ḡiaoga gararoꞌi. Rehano ḡaꞌe fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa radu faine ḡoeroꞌi, faine haḡaoꞌi, vaze zamare borofoꞌi, Iesu mazao hube hune fioꞌi ebu zama deheḡa hina Badiꞌa ubumao haḡai duduḡa haḡaoꞌi. ꞌOugine, fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ḡa tuhutuhuꞌiꞌuma.
\v 13 Vaze ubumao Buka Zaḡoḡa meꞌodoga, haramoga zu ihozoga veize inaroꞌi, onamo eḡeꞌa amiꞌuma.
\v 14 Ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ibite ꞌevoreze ḡae rana teadu Badiꞌa ḡoere rae furenirotene, ḡa Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ḡahunone hidiro. Ḡahunone aꞌe ago reꞌoreꞌonoꞌi.
\v 15 ꞌAhiguḡa niduꞌa ḡaeꞌa zamaḡo niduꞌa hina inare haḡadu ḡaꞌa ufeta ḡuhureꞌetaꞌaꞌe vaze niduꞌa ihozoꞌi.
\v 16 Ḡaboneḡo zu ihoreḡo faine ḡianoꞌi. E ḡateꞌe ꞌaune haḡaoꞌi. ꞌOugine, Badiꞌaꞌa mene ḡae daꞌo, rehano ḡae ihore igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zuni ḡaboziꞌuma.
\c 5
\s1 Ekalesia Azaḡaniꞌa Haḡaiteꞌe Haḡaiḡa moneo Ihoniro
\p 
\v 1 Ohoze vouḡa riḡa ago ronoꞌi, rehano mogo teige iradugunoꞌi. Ohoze izigaꞌe negoḡo teige iradugunoꞌi.
\v 2 Roḡae vouḡaḡaꞌe viꞌu teige iradugunoꞌi. Roḡae izigaꞌe hube hune zamaḡo deheḡa hina ezeḡo teige iraduguzoꞌi.
\p 
\v 3 Dananoga vazeḡa oꞌoꞌa ḡozobaḡa niduꞌa gubazoꞌi.
\v 4 Rehano ḡozoba ꞌahogaꞌe tahiꞌaḡeta ga aḡiḡeta reine, tahiꞌaḡa zu aḡiḡaniꞌa zeḡe neo tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ibite geno taufoꞌi rae ihoziꞌuma.\f + \fr 5:4 \fqa ze ibite Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa haḡaiḡa ederiꞌuma \f* Ebu vize moze zu aḡizeꞌa ubudeze faifairu taufiroteꞌe moneo, ubudeze zuni vize moze zu aḡize mazao baronoꞌi rae ihoziꞌuma, mazaḡa aꞌe Badiꞌa matuꞌohauꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa raꞌohe.
\v 5 Dananoga vazeḡa oꞌoꞌa zu ane daꞌo radiuꞌeteꞌe ḡozobaḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa hube hune ani dananiꞌuma rae mae ḡihineꞌenaꞌa, ohere zu madai ꞌaune umide kurauꞌohe.
\v 6 U iniu raha matuꞌuḡa veize daꞌo radiu tauḡeꞌeteꞌe ḡozobaḡaꞌe ḡaboga rehano, rune ḡozobaḡa raꞌohe.
\v 7 Vazeꞌa ekalesia azaḡaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae mene rozifine, ꞌahiguḡa ekalesia azaḡa ihozoꞌi.
\v 8 Iniu nabuga mene taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zu nabuga boꞌaḡano ane neo tiburu radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mene ufeta taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe aniꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe oꞌoniroteꞌe vazeḡa. Aniꞌe sauꞌa, u mene fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ani vitinoga.
\p 
\v 9 Iniu muriḡa 60 vitinoga zu ḡae tiba daꞌo hahuriroteꞌe\f + \fr 5:9 \fqa ize mazao zama tibano haḡaidoteꞌe \f* ḡozobaḡa reine, ekalesiaꞌa danaziteꞌe ḡozobaḡa nizeo zouziꞌuma.
\v 10 Ebu aniꞌa gau manoḡa haḡadu vazeꞌa niguneꞌeteꞌe ḡozobaḡa rae reꞌuma. Aniꞌe ubugaubuga faine taufiꞌuma, vaze mae zouzadu ḡubuziꞌuma, Badiꞌa mone azaḡa veize tuḡure vazeḡa teige gauꞌiꞌuma, aduga hideꞌeteꞌe azaḡa danaziꞌuma, ebu haḡai manoḡa niduꞌa haḡaifine inariꞌuma.
\p 
\v 11 Ḡozoba iziga roꞌidene ḡozoba nizeo ago toꞌi. Mazaḡa ze ahiri ura haḡaihi rae zamareꞌetene Keriso veize gaueꞌeteꞌe modadu hahurihi raꞌohe.
\v 12 Eꞌanoꞌo ze ibite Keriso mazao ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa variꞌadu vazeꞌa ze sauꞌa haḡairo rae reꞌuma.
\v 13 Ebu zeꞌe tubuḡa radu ne ꞌahogaꞌahogano ragave tauḡeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa hegotiꞌuma. Mene tubuḡa daꞌo, rehano vaze dudiziꞌuma, vaze gauo ḡunuḡuniꞌuma, ebu mene reiteꞌe ḡoeꞌa reꞌuma.
\v 14 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa, ḡozoba iziga bare hahuradu ze ubudeze furezoꞌi ebu neze faine taufoꞌi rae iraduguzeꞌohe. ꞌOugine, ze veꞌoḡa ꞌahoga mene haḡadu agire vazeḡaniꞌa ze rae sausauzoga mene idaḡa reꞌuma.
\v 15 Ḡozoba nuꞌe amahi Keriso modadu Satani hegotiro.
\p 
\v 16 Ekalesia roḡae ꞌahoga, ane nabuga boꞌaḡano ḡozoba nu eꞌe reine, aniꞌa ze danaziꞌuma ebu ekalesia mazao ze danazoga mene umiziꞌuma. ꞌOugine, ekalesiaꞌa iniu danazoga vazeḡa oꞌoꞌa raꞌeteꞌe ḡozobaḡa huga niduꞌa daꞌo danaziꞌuma.
\p 
\v 17 Ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ekalesia faine ibitozine, ekalesia azaḡaniꞌa ze ufeta hune gubaziꞌuma. Zeḡe boꞌaḡano haramo azaḡa zu ihore azaḡa veize ufeta hune gubaziꞌuma.
\v 18 Mazaḡa Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige raꞌohe, “Vazeꞌa boromakau hina vuidi hiriveꞌeteꞌe\f + \fr 5:18 \ft Iuda azaḡa hiriveꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa amahiḡa. Boromakauꞌa vuidi rana oname onaeꞌenaꞌa, vuidi ogaḡa ḡomake vaḡineꞌohe.\f* madaḡano boromakau zuni vuidi afine hebeze ago furuꞌoꞌi,”\x + \xo 5:18 \xt Goro 25:4\x* zu “Gau vazeḡaniꞌa ane gau naeḡa meꞌuma.”\x + \xo 5:18 \xt Luka 10:7\x*
\v 19 Ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa veꞌoḡa haḡadu kotao ohonihi reine, ane veꞌoḡa rae fureneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa aheu ga uḡidu vaḡoꞌi. ꞌUguḡa azaḡa oꞌoꞌa roꞌidene, ani kotao ago ohonoꞌi.
\v 20 Ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa sauꞌa ꞌaune haḡaine, ekalesia azaḡa ubumao rozoꞌi. ꞌOugine, vaze ꞌahogaꞌahoga zuni sauꞌa haḡaoga rihoniꞌuma.
\p 
\v 21 Badiꞌa zu Keriso Iesu ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ohotiroteꞌe tuḡure viga ubumao e riḡa ḡaꞌohe. Ḡoere ꞌadi hegotoꞌi. Ḡaꞌa vaze niduꞌa mazao mene inaheꞌenaꞌa, idane haḡaoꞌi.
\v 22 Ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ohozoꞌidene, zeḡe rana ꞌevoreḡo ago ḡarihe toꞌi. Vaze sauꞌano ago ꞌauḡoꞌi, rehano ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare ḡiaꞌeꞌenaꞌa, deheḡano radiuꞌenoꞌi.
\p 
\v 23 Izidionoꞌo vu isoḡa daꞌo ago gagoꞌi, rehano ḡae isi veize zu ḡae ḡehaḡa maꞌeteꞌe ugiḡaꞌe manoroga veize vaini vuḡa tahiḡa zuni gagoꞌi.
\p 
\v 24 Vaze nuꞌa haḡai sauꞌa furene haḡadu ze ꞌizema kotazogano haḡaize sauꞌaniꞌa fureruꞌohe. U nuꞌa haḡaize sauꞌaꞌe ꞌuꞌuru teadu vesuꞌu fureruꞌohe.
\v 25 Eꞌe teige, haḡai manoḡaꞌe deheru fureranadu vazeꞌa edereꞌohe, ebu haḡai manoḡa ꞌuꞌuruḡa zuni mada ꞌahogano fureranadu vazeꞌa edereꞌohe.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Ekalesia azaḡa boꞌaḡano tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa zeḡe zama niduꞌa hina zuhiꞌaze gubaziꞌuma. ꞌOugine, vazeꞌa Badiꞌa ni zu emeḡe ihore mene rae sausauniꞌuma.
\v 2 Tuḡure azaḡa zeḡe zuhiꞌaꞌe fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa reine, zuhiꞌazeꞌe zeḡe ekalesia nabuga radu mene ovoe ḡiaziꞌuma. Rehano tuḡure azaḡaꞌe zuhiꞌaze veize ufeta gauꞌiꞌuma, mazaḡa zeḡe gauonoꞌo manoḡa hideꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zuni fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Badiꞌa zamarone azaḡa.
\s1 Ḡuriro Ihoreḡa Azaḡa
\p Ḡoere ꞌadi ekalesia azaḡa ihozoꞌi ebu eꞌe hegotifine inare zoꞌi.
\v 3 Vaze nuꞌe ihore ꞌahoga ihozeꞌenaꞌa, emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Keriso ihoreḡa huga zu Badiꞌa gubaneꞌeteꞌe ihoreḡa mene mae ḡihineꞌohe.
\v 4 Ze zeḡeꞌa bare nize mae itadu ḡauni ꞌahoga mene edereꞌohe, zu vaze teite rotetihi zu taꞌirotitihi raꞌohe. Eꞌe uꞌano, ahiahi, roteto, vaze rae sausauzeꞌeteꞌeꞌa fureruꞌohe ebu zamarone sauꞌaniꞌa vaze ꞌadaꞌadazeꞌohe.
\v 5 Ebu zamazeꞌa ufeta sautaro zu ze ihore huga modiro. Eꞌanoꞌo hadi hidoga veize ze Badiꞌa gubaneꞌohe zu zeḡe boꞌaḡano rotetoꞌa ꞌaune fureruꞌohe.
\p 
\v 6 Rehano emeꞌa ḡau niduꞌa moneo idaḡa daꞌo rae zamareꞌenaꞌa, Badiꞌa gubaneꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano radiune, manoḡa boro hidiꞌuma.
\v 7 Eme raha ꞌadao ahiri isoḡa fureraro ebu ahiri isoḡa rudaꞌuma.
\v 8 Eꞌanoꞌo ogomu zu dabuaꞌe emeḡe mazao eꞌe reine, aꞌe idaḡa rae reꞌuma.
\v 9 Maꞌora vazeḡa reihi raꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa sauꞌa haḡaihi rae raꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano uiteꞌohe. Ebu ze ꞌahirizeadu kauriḡa zu zamarone sauꞌa zamaḡano diuḡeꞌohe. ꞌOugadu ze ruizeꞌeteꞌe zu sausauzeꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano uiteꞌohe.
\v 10 Sauꞌa nunu niduꞌaꞌe hadi ubumaḡaonoꞌo fureruꞌohe. Vaze nuꞌa hadi ufeta mouga veize, fieꞌeteꞌe modadu ragaviro ebu aduga boro hidadu zamaze ufeta adudaro.
\s1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa Ḡonaga
\p 
\v 11 Rehano ḡa, Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, haḡai sauꞌa ꞌuguḡanonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi. Ebu Badiꞌa ubumao haḡai duduḡa haḡaoga, Badiꞌa gubanoga zu fioga, vaze zamare borofoga, aduga zamaḡano zamaḡo obone touga, zu roḡeru haḡaoga veize inaroꞌi.
\v 12 Ḡaeꞌa fie gigaruꞌeteꞌe veize faifairu utitoꞌi ebu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu moꞌi. Eꞌe veize Badiꞌaꞌa ḡa huḡadiro, ebu vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ḡae ḡoere igirotene, ḡa zeḡe ubumao ḡaeꞌa fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe huga rae fureniro.
\v 13 Ḡau niduꞌa ḡabone ziniꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa ubumao zu Pontio Pilato ubumao huga daꞌo rae fureniroteꞌe vazeḡa, Keriso Iesu ubumao eḡeꞌa ḡoere ꞌahi riḡa ḡaꞌohe.
\v 14 Ḡa veꞌoḡa ꞌahoga ga vazeꞌa ḡaꞌe roḡaditeꞌe haḡaiḡa ꞌahoga ago haḡaoꞌi, ebu eḡe ḡoere ꞌadi ꞌaune hegotoꞌi, onamo emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu Kerisoꞌa bariꞌuma.
\v 15 Badiꞌaꞌa ohoniroteꞌe madaḡano Keriso tuḡuniꞌuma. Badiꞌaꞌe emeꞌa niguniteꞌe vazeḡa, zu eme Zuhiꞌafiꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa tibuhuga, zu Kini Ḡihiꞌaḡa Hune, zu Zuhiꞌa Boro Ḡihiꞌaḡa Hune.
\v 16 Ani tibuhuga daꞌo mene rudauꞌohe ebu agaḡa huneo radiuꞌohe. Vazeꞌa eꞌe agaḡa uhiḡa hune onamogaꞌe mene idaḡa. Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ani mene horoniro zu horonogaꞌe mene idaḡa. Ani gubanihi. Aniꞌa inaraḡa hina zuhiꞌafiꞌuma, onamo tuḡutuḡu. Amen.
\p 
\v 17 Izidi madaḡano maꞌora azaḡa ꞌahige riḡa zoꞌi. Ze zeḡeꞌa bare nize mene mae itiꞌuma. Ebu mene radiu tuḡutuḡeꞌeteꞌe toheḡa mene zamare borofiꞌuma, rehano eme matuꞌe radoga veize ḡau niduꞌa borofe rifiꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa ufeta zamare borofiꞌuma.
\v 18 Ebu ze haḡai manoḡa zu gau manoḡa ḡehaḡa haḡaiꞌuma, zu ḡahugone zamaroneḡa hina ḡauze zahara azaḡa teite matuꞌe ḡahugiꞌuma.
\v 19 Ze ꞌouge haḡaine, zeꞌa zeḡe veize ḡau manomano adureo ragateragate teadu zama moneo ḡabone huga hidiꞌuma.
\p 
\v 20 Timoteo, Iesuꞌa ḡaniroteꞌe ihoreḡa huga faine ḡianoꞌi. Badiꞌa mene gubaneꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌanonoꞌo zu huga oꞌoꞌa taꞌiroḡanonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi. Edeḡa boro rae ḡuriradu ihore huga hezahohauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi.
\v 21 Ḡuriro ihoreḡa eꞌe rae fureniroteꞌe azaḡa nuꞌe zeḡeꞌa finutaꞌaꞌe modiro.
\p Badiꞌaꞌa zae mazao manoḡa fureneꞌenoꞌi. 
